These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  project-manager, police-officer, architect, entrepreneur, engineer
There 5 different types of food: corn, plum, spinach, strawberry, lime
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: soul, pop, metal, country, jazz
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daffodil, begonia, zinnia, lily, orchid
 1. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the police-officer##1
 3. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 4. the architect is the architect##1
 5. the person who growsdaffodil is the person eating corn##1
 6. the engineer is on the left of the architect##1
 7. the fan soul is on the left of the fan metal##1
 8. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 9. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1
10. the project-manager is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
11. the engineer is between the fan pop and the person eating lime##2
12. the fan country is on the left of the person eating plum##1
13. the fan jazz is on the right of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Job      | project-manager        | police-officer | engineer     | architect   | entrepreneur |
| Food   | spinach     | plum      | strawberry | lime   | corn    |
| Music-Genre   | country  | pop     | soul | metal | jazz  |
| Flower           | begonia | zinnia      | orchid     | lily   | daffodil     |

