.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, september, april, march, november
5 different games are played: bridge, poker, scrabble, canasta, chess
There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, yellow, chestnut, ebony, blood-red
The people have 5 different jobs:  scientist, analyst, police-officer, project-manager, chef
 1. the chef is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the chef##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
 5. the analyst is between the person who likes blue and the person playing chess##2
 6. the project-manager is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the scientist##1
 8. the person who likes chestnut is the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing poker##1
11. the person who likes chestnut is the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the analyst is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Birthday         | march | july | november    | september  | april    |
| Game   | chess    | poker       | scrabble      | bridge | canasta        |
| Color   | blood-red   | yellow     | blue    | ebony  | chestnut     |
| Job     | police-officer    | analyst | chef | project-manager | scientist |

