The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, november, january, february, july
 1. the person traveling to liverpool is the turkish##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1
 3. the pakistani is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the goat is in the middle##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the german##1
 7. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 9. the russian is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in september is the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the person traveling to london is on the right of the indonesian##1
13. the person who's birthday is in july is between the owner of the bird and the person traveling to hannover##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| City         | edinburgh | liverpool     | hannover   | miami   | london |
