 3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the art-deco house is between the person traveling to prague and the owner of the snake##2
 5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the modern house##1
 7. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the person who growslily is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 9. the person traveling to berlin is in the middle##1
10. the person traveling to prague is the colonial house##1
11. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
12. the colonial house is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
13. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
