 5. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 6. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 7. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the fan reggae##1
 8. the fan soul is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the fan d&b##1
11. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
12. the fan blues is on the left of the fan d&b##1
13. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
