.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: animation, action, time-travel, romance, mystery
There 5 different types of food: lime, apricot, pineapple, peas, nectarine
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, game, pall-mall, bongani, bolivar
5 different pets are kept: lizard, cat, frog, rabbit, rat
 1. the bolivar-smoker is between the owner of the cat and the game-smoker##2
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 3. the person watching action movies is the person eating peas##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
 5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 6. the person eating peas is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 8. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 9. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
10. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left##1
11. the owner of the frog is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person eating pineapple##2
12. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
13. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Movie-Genre    | time-travel       | romance    | mystery | action  | animation        |
| Food       | nectarine | lime | pineapple  | peas | apricot    |
| Cigar       | pall-mall        | bongani   | game  | bolivar   | havana |
| Pet   | rabbit       | frog      | rat      | lizard | cat  |

