.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, april, december, october, june
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, skydiving, video-games, rock-climbing, gardening
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, asparagus, pomegranate, apricot, plum
