 1. the craftsman house is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person eating pomegranate and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the right of the palace house##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the tower house##2
 7. the palace house is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is the craftsman house##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
11. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person eating asparagus##1
12. the person eating apricot is on the far left##1
13. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1

