There are 5 different favourite colors: black, orange, ivory, lilac, lavender
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, animation, scientific, epic, action
 1. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 3. the coach is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person who likes orange is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who likes black##2
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
 7. the videographer is between the person watching fantasy movies and the coach##2
 8. the architect is between the nurse and the musician##2
 9. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the musician##1
10. the musician is on the right of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
