.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, lilac, orange, white, amber
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, february, may, october, march
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, fanta, lemonade, coffee
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, iris, rose, lily, daffodil
 1. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who growslily and the person drinking coffee##2
 3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person drinking fanta##2
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person who likes white is the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is the person drinking cola##1
10. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
11. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Color         | orange    | amber  | lilac  | black      | white |
| Birthday   | february    | march   | october | may | december   |
| Beverage   | fanta | almond-milk    | coffee    | lemonade       | cola         |
| Flower   | lily  | iris | daffodil    | rose     | sunflower      |

 